{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/MiniSoulConstruct.gif?t=1737951638\" />\u200a<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/MiniSoulConstruct.gif?t=1737951638\" />\u200a<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/MiniSoulConstruct.gif?t=1737951638\" />\u200a</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A diver sent down into the deepest depths of the vast and treacherous oceans to discover secrets untold. You will face formidable adversaries, ferocious creatures and maybe even some people. Conquer the ocean, lest it conquer you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/ARDUOUS_BIOMES.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The treacherous depths are home to ruthless creatures doing what they can to survive. Anything alive is fair game, and that includes you. Face deadly adversaries that will do everything they can to take you down. Turn the tides, or drown in them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/TITANIC_BOSSES__1_.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge memorable bosses that will put your skills to the test and leave you gasping for air, from the slow-paced and methodical to the breakneck and downright bullet hells. These titans will do whatever they can to annihilate you, but should you prevail, you will be rewarded handsomely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/DEEPER_DOWN.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you dive deeper into the watery depths, challenges will arise. Explore biomes filled with their own unique species, discover items and secrets untold. Stand up to these challenges, or be crushed under the pressure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/UNIQUE_WEAPONS.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a variety of items, from stat steroids to run makers, you will find everything you need down in the depths. Equip insane weapons and test your wit with a dazzling variety of combos and insanely cool mechanics! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What are you waiting for diver? The ocean calls.</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737951638","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737951638","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/b85b150bd0eeb85ce861bff585bca2ead29e9c67/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737951638","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/b85b150bd0eeb85ce861bff585bca2ead29e9c67/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737951638","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3248400,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/MiniSoulConstruct.gif?t=1737951638\" />\u200a<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/MiniSoulConstruct.gif?t=1737951638\" />\u200a<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/MiniSoulConstruct.gif?t=1737951638\" />\u200a</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A diver sent down into the deepest depths of the vast and treacherous oceans to discover secrets untold. You will face formidable adversaries, ferocious creatures and maybe even some people. Conquer the ocean, lest it conquer you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/ARDUOUS_BIOMES.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The treacherous depths are home to ruthless creatures doing what they can to survive. Anything alive is fair game, and that includes you. Face deadly adversaries that will do everything they can to take you down. Turn the tides, or drown in them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/TITANIC_BOSSES__1_.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge memorable bosses that will put your skills to the test and leave you gasping for air, from the slow-paced and methodical to the breakneck and downright bullet hells. These titans will do whatever they can to annihilate you, but should you prevail, you will be rewarded handsomely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/DEEPER_DOWN.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you dive deeper into the watery depths, challenges will arise. Explore biomes filled with their own unique species, discover items and secrets untold. Stand up to these challenges, or be crushed under the pressure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/extras/UNIQUE_WEAPONS.gif?t=1737951638\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a variety of items, from stat steroids to run makers, you will find everything you need down in the depths. Equip insane weapons and test your wit with a dazzling variety of combos and insanely cool mechanics! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What are you waiting for diver? The ocean calls.</strong></p>","developers":["Frizuo","Starpixel Studios"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751120/header.jpg?t=1737951638","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256995369,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256995369/movie480.mp4?t=1737951637","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256995369/movie_max.mp4?t=1737951637"},"name":"Dive The Depths - Official Announcement Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256995369/5d6502472cf08c964ce2dad55d54b5e9f6bbae09/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1737951637","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256995369/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1737951637","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256995369/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1737951637"}},{"highlight":true,"id":257007568,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257007568/movie480.mp4?t=1723788542","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257007568/movie_max.mp4?t=1723788542"},"name":"Dive The Depths - Official Teaser","thumbnail":"https://sha